        Delete vertices from an iterable container.

        INPUT:

         - ``vertices`` - iterator of vertex labels

        EXAMPLE::

            sage: import sage.graphs.base.dense_graph
            sage: D = sage.graphs.base.dense_graph.DenseGraphBackend(9)
            sage: D.del_vertices([7,8])
            sage: D.has_vertex(7)
            False
            sage: D.has_vertex(6)
