        INPUT:

         - ``v`` - a vertex

        EXAMPLE::

            sage: P = DiGraph(graphs.PetersenGraph().to_directed(), implementation='c_graph')
            sage: list(P._backend.iterator_out_nbrs(0))
            [1, 4, 5]

        """
        cdef u_int
